{"tid":2012283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警官會所豪過遊艇會，6億升級公帑埋單","createTime":"2020-05-11T13:57:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T16:50:03.000Z","uid":61282,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1a7442659c40324826379c5629b5685e22f7858e","tid":2012283,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:57:17.000Z","msg":"全文入蘋果睇：<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200511&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60928429\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200511%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60928429&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HYc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=92ff6ed3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200511%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60928429&h=5116d38e\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200511&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60928429</a><br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣警官會所受沙中綫工程影響暫時拆卸，政府以「補償」為由指令港鐵以2.6億元承包會所的拆卸重建工程，另豪擲多3億元大翻新「對面海」的太子警察體育遊樂會，引起社會爭議。《蘋果》取得警官會所的重建圖則，發現新會所的設施大升級，當中包括多間哥爾夫球模擬室及室內練習場、標準泳池則變成「維港無邊際」泳池，旁邊還附設按摩浴池及池畔酒吧；室外草地滾球場也被移至室內，較毗鄰的香港遊艇會更加豪華。工程現已錄得超支3.9億元，所有費用將由沙中綫工程費「埋單」。"},{"pid":"36a1517d9cadc8537930b7d7cc0b0de01c7bf101","tid":2012283,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:57:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cb6831058ad3095c59fd1fc43ce0d026a99ca01","tid":2012283,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:58:28.000Z","msg":"咁正？<br />\n我都去考先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088d7fc6e60479af520888476d62131f8e9427c2","tid":2012283,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:58:34.000Z","msg":"公帑埋單"},{"pid":"36d1aa87832f55f83c479ea1144fad30c5c3a97a","tid":2012283,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4cb6831058ad3095c59fd1fc43ce0d026a99ca01","tid":2012283,"uid":253978,